CREATE TABLE songs (

    duration INT
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE,
    registration_date TIMESTAMP,
    favorite_genre VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE playlists (
    playlist_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    playlist_name VARCHAR(100),
    description TEXT,
    creation_date TIMESTAMP,
    user_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE songs_in_playlists (
    playlist_id UUID REFERENCES playlists(playlist_id),
    song_id UUID REFERENCES songs(song_id),
    added_at TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (playlist_id, song_id)
);

CREATE TABLE user_follows (
    follower_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    following_id UUID REFERENCES users(user_id),
    follow_date TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (follower_id, following_id)
);
